Package LAB_06

Class Button

java.lang.Object
LAB_06.Button
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Interface.Stuff>, Interface.Stuff
public class Button extends Object implements Interface.Stuff
The Button class represents a button object that can be stored inside a Jar. Each button has a color and a diameter in millimeters.

This class implements the Interface.Stuff interface, which allows buttons to be compared by their diameter.
